Test Dataset Title Cleaning

test_title_cleaning.Rd

A utility function to test the title cleaning functionality with various edge cases and examples.

Usage

test_title_cleaning()

Value

A data frame showing original titles and their cleaned versions

Examples

test_title_cleaning()
